<h3><a href='http://soldier-ethicist.blogspot.com/2016/11/war-can-be-experience-of-both-heaven.html'>War can be an Experience of both Heaven and Hell</a></h3>
<p>
   Many combat veterans have a love/hate relationship with their wartime experiences. They love the profound sense of purpose that their liv...
</p>
