<div class='item-snippet'>  by Pete Kilner (@combat_ethics)     Killing the enemies of our country in war is something that has to be done, but it&#8217;s not something tha...</div>
</div>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>
</li>
<li>
<div class='item-content'>
<div class='item-title'><a href='http://soldier-ethicist.blogspot.com/2016/11/the-military-leaders-role-in-mitigating.html'>The Military Leader&#8217;s Role in Mitigating Moral Injury</a></div>
