<h2>Think deeply. Act justly.</h2>
<div class='widget-content'>
<a href='http://core-ethics.com'>
<img alt='Think deeply. Act justly.' height='200' id='Image1_img' src='http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wVkyTbvSHJE/WjfhD7zpBBI/AAAAAAAAJPg/YVteC8n707AYSp-kAxFhLM3hM-l6Rga0QCK4BGAYYCw/s1600/FinalLogo-cropped-01PhiSwordJPG.jpg' width='200'/>
</a>
<br/>
<span class='caption'>Core Ethics, LLC</span>
</div>
<div class='clear'></div>
</div><div class='widget Profile' data-version='1' id='Profile1'>
<h2>About Me</h2>
<div class='widget-content'>
<a href='https://www.blogger.com/profile/16027642894453539902'><img alt='My photo' class='profile-img' height='80' src='//3.bp.blogspot.com/-ERiprD5VCJs/WcxRIVkLCiI/AAAAAAAAJL4/FbF6TY4wS9MOqq2HIaGr_XCx1mUGIxZRgCK4BGAYYCw/s80/tri-photo%2B%25282%2529.jpg' width='80'/></a>
<dl class='profile-datablock'>
<dt class='profile-data'>
<a class='profile-name-link g-profile' href='https://www.blogger.com/profile/16027642894453539902' rel='author' style='background-image: url(//www.blogger.com/img/logo-16.png);'>
Pete Kilner
</a>
</dt>
<dd class='profile-data'>Highland Falls, New York, United States</dd>
<dd class='profile-textblock'>Retired Army officer; five short research deployments to Iraq (03, 07) and Afghanistan (09, 10, 11); Ph.D in Instructional Systems (Penn State); M.A. in Philosophy (Virginia Tech); B.S. in Political Science (West Point); founder of Core Ethics, LLC; married, father of four sons, two of whom have chosen to become Army officers.</dd>
</dl>
